                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    ```

                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    This program creates a simple calculator with addition, subtraction, multiplication, and division operations. It prompts the user to choose an operation and enter two numbers, then displays the result. If the user attempts to divide by zero, it catches the `DivideByZeroException` and displays an error message.C# Calculator Program
